               feloniously forging on the <rs id="t18060917-51-cd273" type="crimeDate">8th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060917-51-off272 t18060917-51-cd273"></join> a certain order for the payment of 150 l. with intention to defraud 
                     <persName id="t18060917-51-victim475" type="victimName">
                        Samuel 
